#: ktorrent/dialogs/fileselectdlg.cpp:285
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"You have deselected the following existing files. You will lose all data in "
"these files, are you sure you want to do this?"
msgstr ""
"ເຈົ້າໄດ້ຍົກເລີກການເລືອກໄຟລ໌ທີ່ມີຢູ່ແລ້ວ. ຂໍ້ມູນທັງໝົດໃນໄຟລ໌ເຫຼົ່ານີ້ຈະສູນຫາຍ, ເຈົ້າແນ່ໃຈບໍ່ວ່າຕ້ອງການເຮັດແບບນີ້?"

#: ktorrent/dialogs/fileselectdlg.cpp:291
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@action:button"
msgid "Delete the Files"
msgstr "ລຶບໄຟລ໌"

#: ktorrent/dialogs/fileselectdlg.cpp:292
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@action:button"
msgid "Keep the Files"
msgstr "ເກັບໄຟລ໌ໄວ້"

#: ktorrent/dialogs/fileselectdlg.cpp:318
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Opening the torrent <b>%1</b>, would share one or more files with the "
"following torrents. Torrents are not allowed to write to the same files. "
"Please select a different location."
msgstr ""
"ການເປີດທໍເຣັ້ນ <b>%1</b>, ຈະເປັນການແບ່ງປັນໜຶ່ງ ຫຼື ຫຼາຍໄຟລ໌ກັບທໍເຣັ້ນຕໍ່ໄປນີ້. "
"ທໍເຣັ້ນບໍ່ໄດ້ຮັບອະນຸຍາດໃຫ້ຂຽນທັບໄຟລ໌ດຽວກັນ. ກະລຸນາເລືອກຕຳແໜ່ງອື່ນ."

#: ktorrent/dialogs/fileselectdlg.cpp:424 ktorrent/dialogs/pastedialog.cpp:62
