#. i18n: ectx: property (toolTip), widget (QCheckBox, kcfg_openMultipleTorrentsSilently)
#: ktorrent/pref/generalpref.ui:129
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"When you select multiple torrents to be opened at the same time, open them "
